OL,3,CMiddlesbrough miss out on promotion as
OL,4,CHull City win in play-off final
OL,6,FHull emerged from the chaos of the
OL,7,FChampionship play-offs to beat
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough in the 'Spygate' final
OL,9,Fat Wembley and seal a return to the
OL,10,FPremier League.
OL,12,FOli McBurnie struck in stoppage time
OL,13,Fto fire the Tigers back to the top-
OL,14,Fflight after nine years.
OL,16,FMcBurnie's goal meant heartbreak for
OL,17,FMiddlesbrough, the side who came in
OL,18,Ffrom the cold after Southampton were
OL,19,Fthrown out of the play-offs for spying
OL,20,Fon them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
