CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1779631868
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough miss out on promotion as
OL,4,CHull City win in play-off final
OL,6,FIt also avoided the threat of more
OL,7,Flitigation from Hull, whose owner Acun
OL,8,FIlicali vowed to take legal action if
OL,9,Fhis side were not promoted.
OL,11,FHis contention was that Hull should
OL,12,Fhave gone up automatically when Saints
OL,13,Fwere expelled, rather than face the
OL,14,Fteam who had lost the semi-finals.
OL,16,FIn the end if was McBurnie who settled
OL,17,Fthe matter by scoring their third
OL,18,FChampionship play-off final winner,
OL,19,Femulating the Dean Windass-inspired
OL,20,Fside of 2008 and Mohamed Diame's class
OL,21,Fof 2016.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1779631868
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough miss out on promotion as
OL,4,CHull City win in play-off final
OL,6,FAfter a week of drama off the field,
OL,7,Fduring half of which Hull did not know
OL,8,Fwho they would be facing, a football
OL,9,Fmatch finally broke out, but the
OL,10,Fopening stages were nothing like as
OL,11,Fenthralling.
OL,13,FBoro dominated but without forcing
OL,14,FIvor Pandur into a single save, with
OL,15,FDavid Strelec heading their best
OL,16,Fchance over.
OL,18,FHull, content to sit in and counter,
OL,19,Fwent close when a header from captain
OL,20,FLewie Coyle had to be helped over the
OL,21,Ftop by Sol Brynn.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1779631868
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough miss out on promotion as
OL,4,CHull City win in play-off final
OL,6,FThe Boro keeper also came out smartly
OL,7,Fto clear the danger when Liam Millar
OL,8,Fraced through, before Mohamed Belloumi
OL,9,Fcurled narrowly wide from 20 yards.
OL,11,FThen, on the stroke of half-time,
OL,12,FMillar's cross found McBurnie whose
OL,13,Fheader deflected off the shoulder of
OL,14,Fdefender Adilson Malanda and hit the
OL,15,FBoro crossbar.
OL,17,FMiddesbrough were back on the attack
OL,18,Fstraight after the break and Morgan
OL,19,FWhittaker's shot was deflected wide
OL,20,Fbefore Matt Targett's corner was
OL,21,Fheaded narrowly over by Dael Fry.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1779631868
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough miss out on promotion as
OL,4,CHull City win in play-off final
OL,6,FHull threatened when another Coyle
OL,7,Fcross found Matt Crooks, but the
OL,8,Fmidfielder's weak header drifted wide.
OL,10,FWith 20 minutes to go Boro boss Kim
OL,11,FHellberg introduced Hayden Hackney,
OL,12,Fthe supposed target of the costly
OL,13,Famateur sleuthing with Southampton
OL,14,Ftrying to find out whether the key
OL,15,Fmidfielder was fit.
OL,17,FBut it was a Hull substitute who
OL,18,Fplayed a major role in the winner,
OL,19,Ffive minutes into stoppage time.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
