PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1779631868
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough miss out on promotion as
OL,4,CHull City win in play-off final
OL,6,FYu Hirakawa jinked his way down the
OL,7,Fleft wing and drilled in a dangerous
OL,8,Flow cross. Brynn dived forward to get
OL,9,Fa hand to the ball but it fell to the
OL,10,Ffeet of McBurnie, who scrambled it
OL,11,Fhome to fire Hull back to the promised
OL,12,Fland.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/6
